{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They couldn't believe that we took such good care of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But then we discovered that-- several things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "How two-faced they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We-- we'd go through these towns, and we-- I'm-- I had an old cross-country ambulance right in the middle of tanks, and I'd be the first Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so, we-- our prisoners, who had been captured by the Germans and marched hard, starved, 25 miles a day-- we'd pick them up, liberate them ourselves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I had the interesting experience of going through a little town, and all the Germans are waving and acting like the-- Lederhosen, Bavarian [INAUDIBLE], how happy we are.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, waving white flags.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the prisoner was sitting with me in the ambulance, said, ha.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They marched us through here a few days ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He said, let's get out and I'll show you some guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He said, I recognize these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He said, that guy threw me a rock in my face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That guy hit us with a bucket of horse manure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That guy hit us with a shovel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were screaming at-- you know, [GERMAN], curse the Jews, Heil Hitler, all the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then we came and they were 180 degrees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So I remember I terrified this particular bunch, I got out a-- a medical tag, an emergency medical tag that we put on the wounded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It looked like something official.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went along saying, wie heisst du?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's your name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I pretended I was taking down names and addresses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all terrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They thought the American had an SS too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But the joke among the Allied forces were the Nazis all evaporated as soon as we crossed the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Me, a Nazi?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've never-- No.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
